info:
Duties and Responsibilities:
1.           Support project communication and implementation 
2.           Complete check and reconciliation of bidding information
3.           Complete monthly bidding analysis update
3.           Finance Digitalization Project support

Qualifications:
1.           Major in accounting, finance, information technology or related field;
2.           Detail oriented and faster learner;
3.           Good communication skill in both English (written and oral) and Chinese;
3.           Passion for learning and improvement;
4.           Experience with SQL, Python & Power BI would be a plus;

Requirements:
3-5 days per week till June end
Available time: Feb 20
Location: Shanghai
